HEADWORD: Servant
<hw>Serv"ant</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To subject.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Servantess</ent>⟦br⟧
